title: Honda Sportrax TRX400EX service manual 99-04
description:
The Honda factory service manual for the Sportrax TRX400EX (aka 400EX) ATV, model years 1999 - 2002.  I don't think they changed much until 2005, so this manual should also be good for 2003-2004 owners.

I spent an afternoon trying to get this off (name of shitty file hosting site) and I figured, fuck them, I'll make a torrent for anyone else who needs this.
